{"tid":544407,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Galaxy S9 將整合虹膜面容辨識","createTime":"2018-01-29T12:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T13:13:24.000Z","uid":66607,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2253f343ba95c78d93b0343dac4573f4f47fcc53","tid":544407,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:59:58.000Z","msg":"「爭咩吖！兩樣溝埋做瀨尿牛丸吖！笨！」這是電影《食神》內的一句經典對白，不過應用在下月發表的 Galaxy S9 亦未嘗不可。在 Samsung 尚未正式推出的 Android Oreo beta 系統內，有 XDA Developers 討論區會員將 Settings App 的 APK 檔破解，發現可能會在 S9、S9+ 推出的新功能。<br />\n<br />\n這個名叫「Intelligent Scan」智能掃描的新功能，據說將面容辨識和虹膜掃描合二為一，期望能夠在極暗或極光環境下，都能夠提升準確和保安程度。現時市面上有售的 Galaxy S8、S8+ 和 Note 8 都配備虹膜掃描功能，但它們的軟件並未提及 Intelligent Scan，估計新功能會在 Galaxy S9 和 S9+ 率先亮相。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/210013/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4523%2F210013%2F1%2F&d=5of6%2Frr%2Bxs%2F2k3BnJCQvUEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=318d083b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/210013/1/</a>"},{"pid":"6e62be6aeb771b508eb6aa6295d8b607af9dd5bc","tid":544407,"uid":162567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"s8 會減到幾多?"},{"pid":"a5c51203facea5e1816f12c3bffc4ad0088ffb94","tid":544407,"uid":144063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e62be6aeb771b508eb6aa6295d8b607af9dd5bc","tid":544407,"uid":162567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"s8 會減到幾多?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"想入手S8 幾會先會趺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}